Presented by Senator LAWRENCE of York.
Printed on recycled paper

1 Be it enacted by the People of the State of Maine as follows:
2 Sec. 1. 35-A MRSA §3209-A, sub-§8, as amended by PL 2023, c. 230, §1, is
3 further amended to read:
4 8. Unused kilowatt-hour credits; rules. To the extent rules adopted under this
5 section provide for the periodic expiration of unused kilowatt-hour credits accumulated by
